## Claude-to-IM Bridge
- **Skill**: `~/.claude/skills/claude-to-im/SKILL.md` (auto-triggered by natural language; subcommands setup/start/stop/status/logs/reconfigure/doctor)
- **Plugin**: `claude-to-im@local` at `~/.claude/plugins/local/claude-to-im/` (created 2026-05-02) — explicit slash commands `/claude-to-im:setup`, `/claude-to-im:start`, `/claude-to-im:stop`, `/claude-to-im:status`, `/claude-to-im:logs`, `/claude-to-im:reconfigure`, `/claude-to-im:doctor`, `/claude-to-im:help`
- Pattern: trivial commands (start/stop/status/logs/doctor) call `bash ~/.claude/skills/claude-to-im/scripts/{daemon.sh,doctor.sh}` directly; interactive commands (setup/reconfigure) delegate to the parent skill via the `Skill` tool
- Config: `~/.claude-to-im/config.env` (mode 600); daemon PID at `~/.claude-to-im/runtime/daemon.pid`; logs at `~/.claude-to-im/logs/`

